*BLDG-CTRL    ; Building Control Data
; bBASE, LEVEL, bBEDROCK, BEDROCKLEVEL, bMASS, bSSFR, bSTORMDUL, bSRTH, iSRTHOPT, [EccenRatio], bLATFLEX ; line 1
